This paper deals with measuring emergent communication in multi-agent systems using deep reinforcement learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.RO (Robotics), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
